	<body>
		<p>Choose the size system for file size measurements :</p>
		<p>
			• <span style="font-weight: 700">SI</span> (International System of
			Units): Uses decimal-based units (e.g., 1 KB = 1,000 bytes, 1 MB = 1,000
			KB).
		</p>
		<p>
			• <span style="font-weight: 700">IEC</span> (International
			Electrotechnical Commission): Uses binary-based units (e.g., 1 KiB = 1,024
			bytes, 1 MiB = 1,024 KiB).
		</p>
	</body>
</html>
